{"id": 1763, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，你觉得在什么情况下一家餐厅可以算得上是“贴心”？", "description": "除了在等位子的时候提供美甲服务，还有好些能做的呢。（题图来自：<白熊咖啡厅>）", "record_count": 7259, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170628161927YM20je7pcDZqyHKB.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-29T03:00:50Z", "options": [{"id": 218112, "content": "女掌事先柜摆好烟和筷子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880087}, {"id": 221184, "content": "只要好吃，只要你不用鼻孔看我，那都成", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076938}, {"id": 217345, "content": "每人一份菜单", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341326}, {"id": 219905, "content": "生意好的时候也能叫到服务员?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918438}, {"id": 219906, "content": "生意好的时候，能够叫到服务员?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918438}, {"id": 217347, "content": "不是歧视单独就餐客户", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914127}, {"id": 227844, "content": "你想干什么的时候服务员就来问你要不要了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098607}, {"id": 217349, "content": "上班的时候面带微笑吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1064326}, {"id": 217350, "content": "衣着得体干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1064326}, {"id": 217862, "content": "提供有质量的食物，服务员有EQ,干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066998}, {"id": 218630, "content": "服务员主动且坚决的阻止客人在店内抽烟！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068876}, {"id": 219142, "content": "干净的调料罐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026373}, {"id": 238854, "content": "卫生间洗手有热水。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143651}, {"id": 217607, "content": "有优惠活动时主动询问顾客要不要用更优惠的方式买单，尊重团购顾客。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066739}, {"id": 265737, "content": "服务员亲切有眼力见", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1265150}, {"id": 217353, "content": "诚实的告诉我一个人吃不了那么多的，不要点了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016384}, {"id": 217613, "content": "有宠物可以抱抱", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066746}, {"id": 220173, "content": "我的天这就是海底捞啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074442}, {"id": 225293, "content": "你们都特么是上帝，而我只有一个要求:好吃??难道不是这样吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1090332}, {"id": 217358, "content": "一个人去海底捞，服务员会在对面放只小熊，还会时不时唠嗑。虽然没遇到过，但真的很暖心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995553}, {"id": 220174, "content": "海底捞算不算？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488245}, {"id": 230670, "content": "能提供一人食", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1110346}, {"id": 217359, "content": "有两人座 四人座 多人座 有很好的空间间隔 干净 服务员不做作", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065512}, {"id": 220175, "content": "胖子来吃，少放点油。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074458}, {"id": 220687, "content": "有娃娃椅 有防滑地板", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076053}, {"id": 217360, "content": "可以远程点菜，订位子，去的时候不用等，直接吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897968}, {"id": 217361, "content": "根据每个人的喜好，特点等等制定的特制晚餐，比如桌布色调，餐具材质花纹，食物口味等，以及各种细节", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066291}, {"id": 217362, "content": "服务员情商高", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046740}, {"id": 218130, "content": "微笑服务。", "image": "img/option/option/20170701234118iYQ8RIlNaB49VL6c.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1067780}, {"id": 245011, "content": "24小时随时能进出的小餐馆，并总会被安排相对独立的空间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1169938}, {"id": 217364, "content": "甜筒冰淇淋会给纸巾拿住", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578681}, {"id": 227348, "content": "只能说海底捞的那种服务值得所有商家学习?举个例子就是排队的时候觉得提供的小零食好吃，问服务员哪里买的，服务员打电话给经理问，经理问采购员，然后采购员再过来告诉详细地址，并且又送了好几包给我，这样的服务不能再好?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135968}, {"id": 217365, "content": "会告诉你有优惠套餐可以选择而不是让你单点", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991755}, {"id": 218389, "content": "点了没上的菜竟可以退！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006363}, {"id": 245013, "content": "egg'n things有单独一页的儿童菜单 点完菜 背面印了勾线画就给小朋友涂色 店员会提供小蜡笔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112418}, {"id": 217366, "content": "每种菜式可以点小份 感觉会很贴心 不会浪费", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169698}, {"id": 216599, "content": "门口放着菜单，让人立刻能决定要不要吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 642, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 216600, "content": "可以点半份的菜，很适合独自吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 946, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 216601, "content": "首先，需要能在手机上提前取号排队", "image": null, "praise_count": 117, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 217881, "content": "服务态度周到，和善可亲，个人觉得服务态度真的很重要，关系到就餐的心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1067083}, {"id": 283929, "content": "小小份，一个人可以点很多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354999}, {"id": 216602, "content": "火锅店用小纸条或者服务员提醒的方式告知每种食材的最佳吃法", "image": null, "praise_count": 301, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 217626, "content": "厕所干净利落", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 840174}, {"id": 220189, "content": "物廉价美不用排队", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113262}, {"id": 222238, "content": "给客人自己看价目表的时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080106}, {"id": 232734, "content": "点完菜可以看看菜品介绍啥的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1118513}, {"id": 217375, "content": "提供一个锁上手机的小盒子，吃饭是个沟通的时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955638}, {"id": 216608, "content": "即使已经成熟客，也能让我吃饭的时候有自己的空间", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 218658, "content": "推荐这个菜今天不是很新鲜，换一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978363}, {"id": 224034, "content": "女生长头发吃东西不方便，会给根橡皮筋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1083308}]}